OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly dry with some bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells and variable cloud in the
OL,8,Fevening. Turning cloudier overnight
OL,9,Fwith a few light showers.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FBright spells and variable
OL,12,Fcloud with the odd light shower in the
OL,13,Fmorning. Drier for a time around the
OL,14,Fmiddle of the day before rain spreads
OL,15,Feast from late afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,18,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,19,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter periods too.
